==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Semicentennial
<hw>Sem`i*cen*ten"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to half of a century, or a period of fifty years; <as>as, a
<ex>semicentennial</ex> commemoration</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Semicentennial</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Semicentennial
<hw>Sem`i*cen*ten"ni*al</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fiftieth
anniversary.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Semichaotic</ent>⟦br⟧
